Python and Javascript are both high level scripting languages that use dynamic typing. A main benefit of using Python is its readability, making it accessible to many developers. Simple built in package management and open source are also a desirable feature of Python, which assist in meeting the demands of the project. Lastly, strong community support are also beneficial in the development process and beyond.


